data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Discover the simple elegance of rural living in this  3-bedroom, 2-bath home on 5 acres in north Canon City, Colorado. Get away from it all in this modest abode! The heart of the home is a large country kitchen, a warm and welcoming space where the aroma of home-cooked meals mingles with the expansive views. The primary bedroom features a soaking tub, dual vanities, and a rejuvenating shower, a perfect place to unwind after a day of exploring the great outdoors. The spacious patio and fenced backyard is a great place to host a barbecue with loved ones or simply savor a quiet afternoon. The property is fenced and cross-fenced with a loafing shed for your animals. A spacious shed with concrete floor provides extra storage space. This home not only offers a simple country lifestyle but also provides convenient access to the essentials of daily life. With easy reach to schools, shopping, dining, and recreational activities, you can relish the charm of rural living without sacrificing modern conveniences. In this modest yet inviting home, you'll find a place where the simple joys of life are celebrated, where the views are as vast as your dreams, and where the peaceful rhythm of rural living becomes your daily soundtrack. Welcome to your tranquil haven in Canon City!
